{
  "texts": [
    "Under this paradigm, intelligence emerges not from a monolith but from a composite system.",
    "At the center of the system lies an orchestrator model, whose Given a task, Orchestrator alternates between reasoning and tool calling in multiple turns to solve it.",
    "Orchestrator interacts with a diverse tool set, including basic tools (web search, functions such as get_flight_status, etc.",
    "), specialized LLMs (coding models, math models, etc.)",
    "and generalist LLMs (GPT-5, Claude Opus 4.1, etc.)."
  ]
}